\* test suffices of an expression
THEOREM T1
<1> SUFFICES T2 BY DEF T1, T2
<1> QED BY DEF T2

\* test scope of use statement

THEOREM T1 /\ T2
<1> USE T1
<1>1 T1
   <2> USE DEF T2
   <2> QED OBVIOUS
<1>2 T2 BY ShouldFail
<1> QED BY <1>1, <1>2


\* test references to different parts of the proof

THEOREM FALSE
<1>1 SUFFICES ASSUME TRUE PROVE FALSE OBVIOUS
<1>2 FALSE BY <1>1, ShouldFail
<1> QED BY <1>2

